briefdescription.para: This type is a template for a data entry field that accepts entries (responses or answers) of any data type, including text, numbers, dates, and Base 64 - encoded blobs (images, sounds, video, other binary formats, etc.). This type cannot contain ListItems, but it may be a child of a Question or a ListItem.
